<P align="left"><FONT size="2">Rhode Island
</FONT>

<P align="left"><FONT size="2">Pursuant to a directive of the Rhode Island Public Utilities Commission
(RIPUC), Verizon Rhode Island filed in July&nbsp;2002 a proposal for a new
