expire in December&nbsp;2002. Following the close of evidentiary hearings in the
case, Verizon Rhode Island and the Rhode Island Division of Public Utilities
and Carriers (Division) filed a stipulation on December&nbsp;6, 2002 resolving all
issues in the case. The principal components of the stipulated plan are:
</FONT>
<P><TABLE width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<TR valign="top">
       <TD width="1%" nowrap align="right"><FONT size="2">&#149;
</FONT></TD>
