       <TD width="1%" nowrap align="right"><FONT size="2">&#149;
</FONT></TD>
 <TD width="1%"><FONT size="2">&nbsp;</FONT></TD>
 <TD><FONT size="2">The company will continue its voluntary funding of a discount program for Internet access for schools and libraries at up
to $2&nbsp;million per year until the earlier of December&nbsp;31, 2004, or the implementation of an alternative funding mechanism
(e.g., legislation);
</FONT></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
<P><TABLE width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<TR valign="top">
       <TD width="1%" nowrap align="right"><FONT size="2">&#149;
</FONT></TD>
