does not regulate Verizon Virginia&#146;s competitive services. The plan does not
regulate profits. In June&nbsp;2001, the VSCC modified the plan and extended the
moratorium on rate increases for basic local telephone service until 2004. The
plan has no expiration date.
</FONT>
<P align="left"><FONT size="2"><I>Verizon Washington, DC Inc.</I>
