<DIV style="width: 100%; border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px;">
<DIV align="left" style="background-color: #777777; padding: 1px"><FONT size="2" color="white">PART II<br>
Item&nbsp;5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Market for Registrant&#146;s Common Equity and Related Stockholder Matters</i></FONT>
</DIV>
</DIV>

<P align="left"><FONT size="2">The principal market for trading in the common stock of Verizon Communications
is the New York Stock Exchange. The common stock is also listed in the United
States on the Boston, Chicago, Pacific and Philadelphia stock exchanges. As of
December&nbsp;31, 2002, there were 1,121,000 shareowners of record.
</FONT>
